ExpSyntax.val: IsMobileClient() AND ((Trim({0,22})<>'' AND {0,21} = 0) OR ({0,1}>0 AND NOT ISNULL({0,1}) OR {0,34} = 'Y')) AND {0,60} <> 'Q'
MlsTrans('BIN and Batch Number already in use')

SQL_STMT_U.val: select a.SysNumber,a.AbsEntry,count(0) Bin,sum(OnHandQty) OnHandQty from ( select n.SysNumber,q.AbsEntry,b.OnHandQty from OBTN n,OBTQ q left join OBBQ b on b.ItemCode=q.ItemCode and b.SnBMDAbs=q.MdAbsEntry and b.WhsCode=q.WhsCode where n.ItemCode=':1' and q.ItemCode=n.ItemCode and q.SysNumber=n.SysNumber and n.DistNumber=':2' and n.U_IDU_Kode_PT=:4 and q.WhsCode=':3' )a group by a.SysNumber,a.AbsEntry

select obbq.BinAbs,obtn.AbsEntry,count(0) Bin,sum(obbq.OnHandQty) OnHandQty from obbq,obtn where obbq.ItemCode=':1' and obbq.WhsCode=':3' and obtn.DistNumber=':2' and obtn.U_IDU_Kode_PT=:4 and obtn.ItemCode=obbq.ItemCode and obtn.DistNumber=obbq.DistNumber group by obbq.BinAbs,obtn.AbsEntry

select obtn.DistNumber,obtn.U_IDU_Brand,obtn.U_IDU_Kode_PT,obbq.BinAbs,obbq.OnHandQty from obtq,obtn,obbq where obtq.ItemCode=':1' and obtq.WhsCode=':2' and obtn.ItemCode=obtq.ItemCode and obtn.SysNumber=obtq.SysNumber and obbq.ItemCode=obtq.ItemCode and obbq.SnBMDAbs=obtn.AbsEntry and obbq.WhsCode=obtq.WhsCode and obtn.DistNumber like '%:3%' :4

select obbq.DistNumber,obtn.U_IDU_Brand,obtn.U_IDU_Kode_PT,obbq.BinAbs,obbq.OnHandQty,obbq.SnBMDAbs Qty2 from obbq,obtn where obbq.ItemCode=':1' and obbq.WhsCode=':2' and obtn.ItemCode=obbq.ItemCode and obtn.DistNumber=obbq.DistNumber and obbq.DistNumber like '%:3%' :4
